modules.description: This module provides arbitrary-precision floating-point arithmetic with operations for high-precision numerical computation, including arithmetic, transcendental functions, rounding control, and exception handling. It works with immutable `mpfr_float` values representing numbers with customizable precision and ternary states, supporting comparisons, decomposition, and special value handling. Specific use cases include scientific computing, financial calculations requiring exact rounding control, and applications needing lossless numeric formatting or specialized mathematical functions like Bessel or Gamma functions.
